LIRC driver for the yaUsbIR V3 USB IR Receiver/Transmitter/Power-On Switch

This is a LIRC userrspace driver for the yaUsbIR V3 USB IR Transceiver based
on the original patch lirc-0.9.0_ya_usbir_v3.5.diff.tar.gz for LIRC 0.9.0

